{"word":"G3180 - μεθοδεία - methodeía - meth-od-i'-ah - Wile","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεθοδεία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>methodeía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>meth-od-i'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Wile"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தந்திரம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to follow up or investigate by method and settled plan"},{"paragraph":"2. cunning arts, deceit, craft, trickery"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G3593 - ὁδεύω - hodeúō - hod-yoo'-o/3593\">G3593</a> [compare &ldquo;method&rdquo;]; <i>traveling over</i>, that is, <i>travesty</i>, (<i>trickery</i>): - wile, lie in wait."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1327 - διέξοδος - diéxodos - dee-ex'-od-os/1327\">G1327</a>, <a href=\"#/G1529 - εἴσοδος - eísodos - ice'-od-os/1529\">G1529</a>, <a href=\"#/G1841 - ἔξοδος - éxodos - ex'-od-os/1841\">G1841</a>, <a href=\"#/G3180 - μεθοδεία - methodeía - meth-od-i'-ah/3180\">G3180</a>, <a href=\"#/G3594 - ὁδηγέω - hodēgéō - hod-ayg-eh'-o/3594\">G3594</a>, <a href=\"#/G3595 - ὁδηγός - hodēgós - hod-ayg-os'/3595\">G3595</a>, <a href=\"#/G3598 - ὁδός - hodós - hod-os'/3598\">G3598</a>"}]}